body:
A practical and lovely little pouch for all of your organizing needs. Great for small craft supplies and tools on the go.

Made from industrial wool felt and eco-printed with eucalyptus. Nylon YKK zipper.

Designed, hand-dyed, and sewn by me in Baltimore. Pieced from scraps in effort to be low waste! This is the exact pouch that you will receive with this listing. 

Approximate dimensions: 5.5 inches wide x 3.5 inches tall x 2.5 inches deep
name: AZ0052-010 Circular pouch - felt - small - eucalyptus
